{"tid":1604963,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"求你地認識地勢啦，唔該！","createTime":"2019-09-30T06:37:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T06:55:26.000Z","uid":319877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b6e7b04c1ef0185cc883c6d31b2d7ce2468f43c6","tid":1604963,"uid":319877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:37:28.000Z","msg":"琴日上街發夢，覺得慢慢多翻小小人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過琴日大家和理非散水果陣，全部唔知道地勢，係甘呢邊有狗，果邊又有狗，係甘衝去跑馬地，不斷跟大隊走，好撚容易比人包同夾撚死，從宜家開始務必熟悉地勢，容易比<br />\n你地散水，又可以比前線撤，<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />宜家開始同我睇地圖！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n光復香港，時代革命。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n去除共黨，港人治港。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n沒有暴徒，只有暴政。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dzcVyOt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdzcVyOt.jpg&h=accefa39&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2a62d98151f7f1b1334962198906e460955c5631","tid":1604963,"uid":319877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:39:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34c0a315d8c9e57c647e6d4855ce1a30989d5a7d","tid":1604963,"uid":319877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:39:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82c5c98faddbbb3ed268885da48f0354b2bb7be1","tid":1604963,"uid":319877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:42:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ca8330b1bf516b872b3d835a51c65a52484dca5","tid":1604963,"uid":319877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:42:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"h